{"tid":2491952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[旺角呢間酒樓阿姐同副總經理咁撚吋？] 應該得到阿布泰式懲罰！","createTime":"2021-04-16T16:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T16:41:32.000Z","uid":321893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53245c58d362822a4d43519ff789b392bc160528","tid":2491952,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"阿姐咁撚型！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmezvKnJ9urw9xRh9riBBCUp1RTSrjacYa1PYDMeVG7fad?filename=NgdCt7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgdCt7Y.jpg&h=37798222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n副總經理咁體諒員工咁撚吋！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ8bz1BxyEGcGkPL3b6TuzXpKiHwiFRKMmbvMunqtr5d3?filename=BXM8AOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXM8AOb.jpg&h=78187851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒樓副總經理：「我有二百伙記，有一個冇打嘅，已經係停牌格勒，但係你話選擇唔打嘅，而家大家捱住先咯，四個先咯，唔強求架，好難強求架。」<br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8Lj8uLhPgU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw8Lj8uLhPgU&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=350fb8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8Lj8uLhPgU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">既然阿姐同副總經理咁吋，我地係咪應該四個四個咁去呢間酒樓排隊飲茶呀！佢哋應該得到阿布泰般懲罰，其他公司就可以仿效，唔好逼員工打針，你覺得係咪呀？係仲唔去排隊飲茶！唔去飲茶都幫手推啦喂！</span></span>"},{"pid":"42ed2faf96134e5378d89876cc0219838f6eaf6d","tid":2491952,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"但係有無人知呢間旺角酒樓喺邊度？咩名？"},{"pid":"6d9aba6c807239d488bea473eed8db7b97b43c6f","tid":2491952,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"775975a3e4450ef020a21ff8e42ad74a130748f8","tid":2491952,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}